        <item>
            <id>https://www.ithome.com/0/850/813.htm</id>
            <title>魅蓝 lifeme HD1 耳放上架：双 CS43131 DAC、双端输出，341 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/850/813.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/850/813.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Mon, 05 May 2025 10:25:18 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D855061" rel="nofollow">打磨时光</a> 的线索投递！</div>
            <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 5 月 5 日消息，魅蓝 lifeme HD1&nbsp;耳放现已在京东上架，该耳放主打“双&nbsp;CS43131&nbsp;芯片、飞秒晶振、双端输出”，定价为&nbsp;369&nbsp;元，<strong>首发价 341 元</strong>。</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/ggHGeoO" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/276533/16/27701/110756/680b4fa1F47a28f1b/e2c69d95334a0f90.jpg" title="魅蓝 lifeme HD1 耳放上架：双 CS43131 DAC、双端输出，341 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">魅蓝 lifeme HD1 耳放</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">券后 341 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 8 元券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="3038" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/5/e3f83220-508d-481d-865b-320f8b4820fa.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="魅蓝 lifeme HD1 耳放上架：双 CS43131 DAC、双端输出，341 元" width="808" /></p><p>据介绍，这款耳放外观方面采用哑光黑配色，使用高导热合金阳极氧化铝工艺外壳，耳放内置 2 颗 CS43131 DAC&nbsp;芯片，至高支持&nbsp;PCM 384KHz / 32bit&nbsp;及&nbsp;DSD256&nbsp;的数字音频编解码，同时配备飞秒晶振式中，可改进听感体验。</p><p>此外，该耳放配备了高增益实体开关，用户推动开关即可将平衡端口输出功率提升至&nbsp;162mW。耳放同时配备&nbsp;3.5mm / 4.4mm&nbsp;双接口，号称获得了&nbsp;Hi-Res&nbsp;金标认证。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="2754" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/5/0e3ece32-77e8-4c91-87b7-484e2ac4b192.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="魅蓝 lifeme HD1 耳放上架：双 CS43131 DAC、双端输出，341 元" width="810" /></p><p>IT之家附耳放参数信息如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="3072" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/5/88d376d2-02ae-4012-893d-f5a55b874bc5.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="魅蓝 lifeme HD1 耳放上架：双 CS43131 DAC、双端输出，341 元" width="806" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="2760" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/5/da34ab29-